    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>to the dish with your <strong>tortiglioni</strong>,<strong> Chinese rice wine </strong>and 350ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Nestle the pasta into the water as much as you can, then stir everything together and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
