    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cover with a lid and put the dish in the oven for 25-30 min or until the pasta is cooked through</p><p>Use this time to clear up, set the table, have a cup of tea or simply chill!</p><p>Tip: Give everything a stir halfway through for evenly cooked pasta!</p>",
