    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the pasta is cooked, remove the dish from the oven and stir through your<strong> crème fraîche</strong> and<strong> grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Add the juice of <strong>half</strong> your<strong> lemon[s] </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Taste for seasoning, adding more<strong> salt</strong> if needed<strong> </strong>– this is your <strong>oven</strong> <strong>baked creamy chorizo & leek pasta</strong></p>",
